snippet.title: Zack Snyder Considers Hiring Emilia Clarke instead of Amber Heard
snippet.description:
►Zack Snyder Considers Hiring Emilia Clarke instead of Amber Heard
The majority of people believe that Zack Snyder's Justice League exists just to boost HBO Max subscriber numbers. Although 70 million dollars may appear to be a large sum for a remake of a failed film, Netflix and Disney have frequently spent more on exclusive streaming material. Zack Snyder discusses Amber Heard's exclusion from all DC films. Indeed, if Warner Bros. had been sold on Snyder's initial concept, he wouldn't have had Joss Whedon reshoot 95 percent of the film after Snyder had left the project.
